<ab facs="#facs_271_r1l3"><expan>ʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr vnd ~ der von Gych ſein etc / das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_271_r1l4">Vnd ſein vns ſölıch ſtöſſ <expan>ʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr niht lıeb vnd daʒ das gütlıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_271_r1l5">abgıeng vnd berıcht wurd . das ſehen wır <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> teyls <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> . Vnd wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_271_r1l6"><expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . <expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Erenfrıd<ex>en</ex></expan> von Sekendorff <expan>hawbtm<ex>an</ex></expan> des <expan>lantfr<ex>ids</ex></expan> dıe ſache </ab>
